h1. ApiResponse

h2. Purpose

Documents a error response code

h2. Usage

Simple Usage

{code}
@ApiResponse(code=404, message="These are not the droid you're looking for", response=CustomErrorClass)
{code}


h2. Parameters

{table}
*Parameter*     | *Supported*   | *Usage*
@code@          | Yes           | The HTTP code in question
@message@       | Yes           | The correct interpretation of this code
@response@      | Yes           | The data type of the response during this code
{table}